  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1663170/extras/cd0242e2ca7ffa9645f67b8c3e09d8ca.avif?t=1747315662\" width=616 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong> Have your own air transport company <strong> </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Transport cargo through the skies, buying and managing your airplanes and your team.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Coordinate cargo transportation and earn money</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Choose the best airplanes and complements at the dealership and make your hangar in the best way for you and your company.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Hire and control your employees and have the best people at your side to help the company grow.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Manage your properties and expand your business.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Control your finances and invest your surplus money in the bank, or in difficult times try to get a loan from the bank manager.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Sign transport contracts and transport things massively, earning a lot of money </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> Be a transportation entrepreneur, with control over everything in your business. Work, earn, invest and expand! </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1663170/extras/5dadfef55cc3bc520af3f7daea41287e.avif?t=1747315662\" width=616 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> Success is a few steps away, are you ready? </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> <i> Deal closed! </i> </strong></p>",
